1. WideDeep model (wider + larger embedding);
2. DNN hidden units: [1024, 512, 256] (更宽);
3. embedding size = 16 (加倍);
4. use_wide = False, net_dropout = 0.4 (降低dropout);
5. batch_size = 256;
6. adam_learning_rate = 5e-6 (降低学习率);
7. 训练数据: 2026-03-08 ~ 2026-03-10 (v16样本);
8. 验证数据: 2026-03-11;
9. 假设: 更大的embedding和更宽的网络能提升特征表达能力;
